			<div class="gallerytext"><i>The Belgian soldier devotes himself to his mortally wounded leader</i></div>
		</li>
		<li class="gallerybox" style="width: 376.66666666667px">
			<div class="thumb" style="width: 374.66666666667px;"><span typeof="mw:File"><a href="/wiki/File:Monument_aux_pionniers_belges_au_Congo_02.JPG" class="mw-file-description" title="Allegory of the Congo river"><img alt="Allegory of the Congo river" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/d3/Monument_aux_pionniers_belges_au_Congo_02.JPG/960px-Monument_aux_pionniers_belges_au_Congo_02.JPG" decoding="async" width="375" height="180" class="mw-file-element" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/d3/Monument_aux_pionniers_belges_au_Congo_02.JPG/1280px-Monument_aux_pionniers_belges_au_Congo_02.JPG 2x" data-file-width="3672" data-file-height="1766" /></a></span></div>
